FBIS4-21802 "jptot014__l94102" JPRS-TOT-94-014-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 26 March 1994 CENTRAL EURASIA GEORGIA Explosion on Roof of Independent TV Company in Tbilisi Explosion on Roof of Independent TV Company in Tbilisi Damage, No Casualties LD2603133594 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1100 GMT 26 Mar 94 LD2603133594 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] At 0430 this morning an explosion occurred in Tbilisi on the roof of a six-storey building that houses the Iberviziya independent television company. At the Georgian interior minister's press center it was said that as a result, a satellite aerial was rendered inoperative and was blown from the roof onto the street. Window panes in the building were broken. There are no casualties. The explosion is being investigated.
